sieve-mode.el is a mode for the mail filtering language Sieve. See http://www.cyrusoft.com/sieve/ for more information.

* Homepage: http://josefsson.org/sieve/
* Tutorial: http://josefsson.org/sieve/tutorial.html
* sieve-mode with [[Gnus]]: http://josefsson.org/sieve/gnus-sieve.html
* Manual for the sieve-mode: http://josefsson.org/sieve/sieve.html

sieve-mode is bundled with [[Gnus]] since Oort Gnus.
